<h3 id=3D"WestpacOneCore(CCMP)CoreSystemRouting-3.FindingTheArrangementMast=
erSystemID"><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">3. Finding The Arrangeme=
nt Master System ID</span></h3>
<p><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">In this stage, the API retrieves =
the Master System ID for each arrangement using the retrieved CPC from prev=
ious step. Master System ID will be used by CCMP CAP API for routing the ar=
rangements to the right core system.</span></p>
<p><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">Mesh link: <a class=3D"external-l=
ink" href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/inf-bnkng-prod-sal=
esproddefn-v2" rel=3D"nofollow">https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis=
/inf-bnkng-prod-salesproddefn-v2</a></span></p>
<h5 id=3D"WestpacOneCore(CCMP)CoreSystemRouting-POST/products"><span class=
=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">POST /products</span></h5>
<ul>
<li><span class=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">Base URL: /inf/bnkng/prod/salesp=
roddefn/v2</span></li>
</ul>
